#==============================================================================
# SECTION 3: CYBERAV3NGERS ICS/OT TARGETING
# MITRE ATT&CK: T1071.005, T1572, T0831 (Manipulation of Control)
# Group: IRGC-CEC / BAUXITE (Dragos designation)
# Context: Stage 2 ICS Kill Chain capability confirmed; 400+ devices
#          globally; IOCONTROL deployed across PLCs, HMIs, routers, cameras
